CS:Source Code Name Otter. 

by Chris 'slayerA' Powell

Mission: 

Terrorist: The terrorist have found an abandoned bunker and are in the amidst of resuppling the base. Geologist suverying the area stumbled on top the the terrorist, only to be held hostage, and are barred inside the storage room.  The terrorist are now posted up on their HQ finallizing plans. Protect the hostages from recovery at all or eliminate all counter-terrorist.


Couter-Terrorist: A group of suspected terrorist maybe responsible for kidnapping and holding a small group of geologist that where in the area. The counter-terrorist have been watching the base under Operation Condor, but plans have been moved forward to sweep the base by a waterfront insertion, Code Name Otter...

Rescue any hostages found and return them to one of two hostage rescue points before time runs out or eliminate all terrorist.
